'''近鸟龙科'''（[[学名|学名]]：Anchiornithidae，意为“接近鸟类”）是[[真手盗龙类|真手盗龙类]]的一个科，可能是演化支[[鸟翼类|鸟翼类]]中[[鸟类|鸟类]]最基础的一科（一般意义上）。<ref name="desc">{{cite journal | last1 = Foth | first1 = C. | last2 = Rauhut | first2 = O. W. M. | title = Re-evaluation of the Haarlem Archaeopteryx and the radiation of maniraptoran theropod dinosaurs | journal = BMC Evolutionary Biology | volume = 17 | issue = 1 | page = 236 | date = 2017 | doi = 10.1186/s12862-017-1076-y | pmid = 29197327 | pmc = 5712154 }}</ref>该科被置于[[真手盗龙类|真手盗龙类]]演化树中的不同位置，一些科学家曾将其分类为一个不同的科、[[伤齿龙科|伤齿龙科]]的一个基础亚科、<ref name=Xiaotingia>{{cite journal |author=Xing Xu |author2=Hailu You |author3=Kai Du |author4=Fenglu Han |name-list-style=amp |title=An ''Archaeopteryx''-like theropod from China and the origin of Avialae |url=http://www.ivpp.ac.cn/qt/papers/201403/P020140314389417822583.pdf |date=2011-07-28 |journal=Nature |volume=475 |pages=465–470 |doi=10.1038/nature10288 |issue=7357 |pmid=21796204 |access-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220071919/http://www.ivpp.ac.cn/qt/papers/201403/P020140314389417822583.pdf |archive-date=2016-12-20 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=leeetal2011>{{cite journal|author=Lee, M. S. Y.|author2=Worthy, T. H.|name-list-style=amp |title=Likelihood reinstates ''Archaeopteryx'' as a primitive bird|journal=Biology Letters|volume=8|issue=2|pages=299–303|doi=10.1098/rsbl.2011.0884|pmid=22031726|pmc=3297401|year=2011}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author1=Stephen L. Brusatte |author2=Graeme T. Lloyd |author3=Steve C. Wang |author4=Mark A. Norell |year=2014 |title=Gradual assembly of avian body plan culminated in rapid rates of evolution across the dinosaur-bird transition |journal=Current Biology |volume=24 |issue=20 |pages=2386–2392 |doi=10.1016/j.cub.2014.08.034 |pmid=25264248}}</ref><ref name=Shenetal20172>{{Cite journal|author1=Cai-zhi Shen |author2=Bo Zhao |author3=Chun-ling Gao |author4=Jun-chang Lü |author5=Martin Kundrát |year=2017 |title=A New Troodontid Dinosaur (''Liaoningvenator c